DPM_TEAM04.test

Class TrackWidthTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • DPM_TEAM04.test.TrackWidthTest

  • public class TrackWidthTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Test class to find the best Track width. Must be performed after the Wheel radius test class. The robot will execute 10 laps on itself. If it does not complete the 10 laps, the @Resources.TRACK must be grater. If the robot complete more than 10 laps, the @Resources.TRACK must be decreased.
    Author:
    Tristan Toupin
